text: Innocent Muchaneka (born 3 August 1991) is a Zimbabwean footballer who plays as a midfielder for CAPS United and the Zimbabwe national football team. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Hwange Colliery F.C. players Category:Chicken Inn F.C. players Category:CAPS United players Category:Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League players Category:Zimbabwean footballers Category:Zimbabwe international footballers Category:Association football midfielders
